A little bit more about TemplateMonster Affiliate Program

   Do you know that thousands of people benefit from a cash flow brought
   by different affiliate programs? Do you want to partner up with
   TemplateMonster via our affiliate program? In this case, you have
   chosen the right place to visit. We are here to guide through the world
   of our affiliate program. Join our huge affiliate family and start
   capitalizing profit!

Who Can Benefit From Being a Part of TemplateMonster Affiliate Program?

     * If you are a blogger, it will be a great chance to monetize your
       blog. We have prepared multiple ways to make your affiliate
       campaign stand out from the crowd. However, do not hurry. You will
       find about them a little bit later.
     * Each web-designer and developer can also get the highest earning
       potential together with our affiliate program.
     * We have not forgotten about Internet marketing consultants. You are
       also free to get involved and increase your earnings without any
       effort.

In a Few Words About Our Commission Plan

     * You will get a 30% commission on the first purchase made using your
       affiliate link.
     * You will get a 10% commission on the next purchases.

Your Onward Affiliate Program: Ultimate Checklist of Key Facts

     * To start with, we provide our affiliates with a 30-day return
       policy. In addition to this, you will get the first-click
       interaction. What do all of these words mean? Everything is simple.
       The first cookie set in the given browser will track any credit for
       the referral.
     * It does not matter what language you speak. Our website is
       translated into such languages as German, French, Italian, Turkish,
       Polish, Portuguese, Russian, and Spanish.
     * Are you interested in getting a discount some items featured on
       TemplateMonster? Just use your commission money.
     * Our cookies are valid for 60 days. They run on all sorts of
       products available in our collection (from WordPress themes to
       website templates).
     * There are different payment methods to choose from. These are
       WebMoney, Paypal, SWIFT, Skrill, and Payoneer.
     * Do you have a friend who wants to become an affiliate? Then,
       recruit him or her and get your life-long supervisor’s 5% cut.

Our Affiliate Tools: Which One Do You Need?

   We have promised to speak about some affiliate tools. Get ready to
   discover all of them and make money on them:
     * referral link;
     * collection of WordPress plugins;
     * ready-to-use showcases;
     * banners;
     * landing pages;
     * WebAPI;
     * widgets.

Get in Touch With Us!

   By the way, our trained affiliate team is always ready to help. It
   works round-the-clock and knows the answers to all your questions. In
   the worst-case scenario, to the biggest part of them. Anyway, all
   questions related to our affiliate program will be answered
   immediately. Let us introduce our team and explain who can assist you
   in your issues.
     * Michael Druzhba is an administrator and leading expert in affiliate
       marketing.
     * Victoria Curly, Lana Miro, Alla Taff, Nannie Nova are Affiliate
       Managers, who can assist you with anything you need for promoting.
     * Marina Black is an affiliate support manager who will answer all
       your questions about our affiliate program.
     * Julia McHale is a content manager. She will also help with your
       content and transform your posts into engaging ones.
     * Max Carroll is a Youtube manager who is interested in making your
       channel bring you more money.

   We are speaking to you, the next affiliate who will make a lot of
   money.

   We would be very happy if you sign up for our TemplateMonster affiliate
   program. It seems to us that it has been waiting for you for so long.

